title: AI Search -  KeyPush
introduction: KeyPush is an AI and web search companion that utilizes either Bing or ChatGPT to provide the best search results based on user queries.
features: Uses Bing or ChatGPT for search results
Allows users to force a specific search engine by typing 'b ' for Bing or 'c ' for ChatGPT
Provides information on best phones, stock market trends, trending global topics, and NASA news
targetPeople: General internet users looking for enhanced search capabilities

faqs.question: How does KeyPush decide which search engine to use?
faqs.answer: KeyPush uses either Bing or ChatGPT based on which is best for the search query.

faqs.question: Can I force KeyPush to use a specific search engine?
faqs.answer: Yes, you can type 'b ' before your search to use Bing or 'c ' to use ChatGPT.

faqs.question: What kind of information can I find using KeyPush?
faqs.answer: You can find information on the best phones, stock market trends, trending global topics, and NASA news.
